    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >造物师是一个使用物品战斗的职业，通过击杀怪物掉落物品，收集物品，创造物品，建造自己的领地，防御怪物的攻城。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >例如陷阱-弹射板子可以通过设置弹射方向和距离通过两块板子接力弹射一直弹死怪物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/a2a1aaaa42868bbfa708b66b7c4a86c7.poster.avif?t=1750680269\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/a2a1aaaa42868bbfa708b66b7c4a86c7.webm?t=1750680269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/a2a1aaaa42868bbfa708b66b7c4a86c7.mp4?t=1750680269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >例如 机关-飞轮 它可以前自己的前面8米处发射一个来回的飞轮，飞行过程中会对发生碰撞的怪物进行伤害和流血buff。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/1aa30cbecfe0b566c2762865f4ab7f9d.poster.avif?t=1750680269\" width=412 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/1aa30cbecfe0b566c2762865f4ab7f9d.webm?t=1750680269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/1aa30cbecfe0b566c2762865f4ab7f9d.mp4?t=1750680269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >例如 机关-弹射球 它对怪物进行最多5次接力弹射伤害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/5a17183bc4d80f123d9fda0d118a9d01.poster.avif?t=1750680269\" width=412 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/5a17183bc4d80f123d9fda0d118a9d01.webm?t=1750680269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/5a17183bc4d80f123d9fda0d118a9d01.mp4?t=1750680269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >例如 电网塔 它可以和其他电网塔组成雷电大阵利用雷球来攻击敌人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/4baa5db37ea1cc8244da91c4be070274.poster.avif?t=1750680269\" width=412 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/4baa5db37ea1cc8244da91c4be070274.webm?t=1750680269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/4baa5db37ea1cc8244da91c4be070274.mp4?t=1750680269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >例如 飞剑塔 剑若游鱼穿梭不息快速击杀敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/5c5fe88abd69056ecfd769461de7335f.poster.avif?t=1750680269\" width=412 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/5c5fe88abd69056ecfd769461de7335f.webm?t=1750680269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183400/extras/5c5fe88abd69056ecfd769461de7335f.mp4?t=1750680269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
